<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td colspan="1" valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5" color="black">
    Kelin`s Lugubrious Lament</font></td>
    <td colspan="2" valign="top" align="left"><font color="black"><img
    src="http://205.229.72.28/ev1/public_html/images/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right"></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan = "3">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=127">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=127">
    <small><font color="#000080" face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
    
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    This song essentially causes a single MOB to not attack you. It is useful in
situations where there are two mobs but you can only handle one at a time.
You target the MOB you don't want to attack and then play this song. Once
the sparkles appear around the MOB, you have a small number of seconds to
attack the other MOB and lead it away. The effect only lasts for a few
seconds so be quick.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B> Kelethin<BR>
<B>Skill:</B> Stringed Instruments<BR>
 
<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Target: Lower Reaction Range & Frezy
    </font>
    
    </td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">
    
			&nbsp;<br>
			&nbsp;<br>
			Mana:<br>
			Casting Time:<br>
			Target Type:<br>
			Level:<br>
			Rank:<br>
    </font></td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">

		  &nbsp;<br>
		  &nbsp;<br>
			0<br>
			3<br>
			Target<br>
			8<br>
			1<br>
    </font></td>
  </tr>
