			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I'm afraid that description was difficult for me to understand.  Here's my understanding of it and how I have succesfully used it.<BR>
<BR>
In an area where creatures spawn in place (Dervish camps, Orc camps, etc.) this spell can make one creature (your target) not attack with the creature group for the duration they are lamented.<BR>
<BR>
So the strategy is to use this song on some one creature and pull the rest.  After you finish the mob, you can go back for the one creature remaining.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
