	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Er, his description is not quite accurate. This song causes a MOB to become non-hostile and ignore cries for help from others nearby. It seems to last about 20-30 seconds. It is much harder for monsters to resist than spell equivalents. (Lull and such.) Even yellows usually cannot resist it. Furthermore, if you stand far enough away, the MOB will not attack you even if he resists! (It has to be near the range limit for this to work.) The way to use this song is to sing it at every MOB except the one you want to attack, then draw that one safely away. Lather, rinse, repeat. Beware, though, sometimes when a monster resists this, ALL nearby laments will be broken. (Is this a bug or a feature?) This song is incredibly useful. With it, I was able to solo the orc camps near freeport at level 10. These normally require a group of level 12s. Just have Selo's accelerando handy when you first try it out, cause your gonna mess things up the first few times. =)
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
