	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is a great song.  Makes soloing a whole lot easier and people will love you for it.  I keep on using it and i'm into my 21 level for when i need to break up some critters.  If there is any wisunderstanding, the meaning of what the song does is very simple-sing this to any creature that you don't want to come after you once you attack it's buddies.  A few misunderstadings with the song-casting this on a critter that cons &quot;ready to attack&quot; does not make them not want to attack you.  If you cast it on them and get close they still will attack.  This is not an area effect song so you have to cast it on the individual critters that you don't want to attack you.  When you do cast it, make sure that the creature doesn't resist it-most won't (the only ones that do are really high red creatures) but make sure that you look before you attack because if they resist it and you attack it, yes they will still attack you.  
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
